### LXXXVIII. HOW A MAN THAT AT IS PROVIDING HIS OWN TOMB.

<span id="img_13900"></span> ![](img/13900.jpg)

When they would symbolise *a man that is providing* 

<span id="page_140">p. 140</span>

*his own tomb*, they depict an ELEPHANT <span
id="fr_138"></span>[1](#fn_133.md) BURYING ITS OWN TEETH; for when his
teeth fall out, he takes them up and buries them.

